"So far, this covers only a few ferries on the Danube, but there are <a "
"href=\"https://git.lw1.at/lukas/route.lw1.at/src/branch/synced/main/own_gtfs/ideas.md\">many"
" more possibilities</a>."
msgstr ""

#: templates/faq.html:324
msgid "What is the usage policy? How can I use this website?"
msgstr ""

#: templates/faq.html:326
